data.description: Looking for a quick move-in? Come see this stunning 3/2.5 home in the Woodlake subdivision. NO CARPET ANYWHERE! The home is turn-key ready with plenty of upgrades the whole family will enjoy. Open floor plan, with large family room, formal dining room, and eat-in kitchen. Upstairs, you'll find 3 well-sized bedrooms along with 2 full baths and a spacious loft. The large primary bedroom has a garden tub, separate shower, double vanity, and walk-in closet. You will appreciate the newly installed, serene backsplash. The second floor also boasts an inviting loft/family/game room, providing a versatile space that can be customized to suit your lifestyle. Beautifully landscaped front yard with newly done tiled porch offers great curb appeal. A covered patio and a newly tiled back porch in the backyard are perfect for entertaining. With its prime location, this home provides easy access to shopping, schools, and the nearby I-10. Only a few minutes away from Randolph AFB and Fort Sam AB. This home comes with a host of additional upgrades that enhance its appeal. Per the owner, the roof was replaced in 2019 and the water heater in 2022. Please see the additional list of upgrades. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours. Book your showing today!
